fields.customfield_12215: /HGW/Webui/Common/My WiFi/Advanced WiFi/Different configuration for WiFi 5GHz and WiFi 2.4 GHz

fields.Action: From the WebUI, try to Switch OFF the WiFi on 5Ghz band.
fields.Expected Result:
Expected Result 
It should be possible to switch OFF the Wifi on 5Ghz band.
The SSID should be no more visible on 5Ghz

"Use a tool like InSSider to confirm"

fields.Action: From the WebUI, try to Switch ON the WiFi on 5Ghz band.
fields.Expected Result:
It should be possible to switch ON the Wifi on 5Ghz band.
The SSID should be visible on 5Ghz

"Confirm that is working by connecting a station to with and verifiyng connectivity"

fields.description:
The test aims to check the ability to Switch WiFi on and off using the WebUI
	 

[Precondition]

	Wifi is Active
	Different Configuration for 2.4GHz and 5GHz is chosen on the Webui.

security.description: Only SoftAtHome people can access the issue
